Magda Fontanges https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Magda_Fontanges 0 Magda Fontanges (10 May 1905 – 1 October 1960), also known as Madeleine Coraboeuf, was a French actress, journalist and a spy for the Germany Secret Service between 1940 and 1943.
